Package com.opengamma.strata.examples

High level examples of Strata.

This package contains the high-level examples of using Strata. More examples can be found in com.opengamma.strata.examples.finance, including examples of calibration, scenarios and trade construction.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlogsTest
    Test blog related examples do not throw exceptions.
    DsfPricingExample
    Example to illustrate using the engine to price a Deliverable Swap Future (DSF).
    ExamplesTest
    Test examples do not throw exceptions.
    FraPricingExample
    Example to illustrate using the engine to price a FRA.
    FxPricingExample
    Example to illustrate using the engine to price FX trades.
    GenericSecurityPricingExample
    Example to illustrate using the engine to price generic securities.
    StirFuturePricingExample
    Example to illustrate using the engine to price an Ibor Future (STIR).
    SwapPricingExample
    Example to illustrate using the calculation API to price a swap.
    TermDepositPricingExample
    Example to illustrate using the engine to price a Term Deposit.
